
Cloud --> 3 model darad:
1. cloud storage
2. cloud process
3. Green computing

*********************************

Green computing yek chizi shabihe claseringe ba in tafavot ke ke sistem ra mikonim 4 system

Har kodom az in system ha yek kar ra mikonad.
Masalan yeki + mikone yeki - va yeki * va yeki \
Ke dar in halat ham baz yek LB (Loud balancer) darim ke in bar ra taghsim mikone
Va zamanike ma darkhaste + darim miravad dar LB va bad LB az systeme + migirad

**********************************

in halat ha ---> halate Offline va Online darad

********************'
Corba ---> bayad zabane hardotaraf yeki bashe va bayad C ya az khanevadeye C mesle C++ bashad.

!!! zabane C ---> RMI ra ghabool nemikonad.

*************************************************

web service : 1. Soap     2.Rest

2. Rest  ---> web service haye saritari hastand va berooztarann va amniate balaie daran
1. Soap  ---> web service ghadimitar va kondtare va niaz be Client daran.

*******************************''

RMI (Remote Method Invocation) ---> har do system bayad ye zaban dashte bashand.

Server va Client ra khodemon minevisim va harkodam dar ye jaye digast ke ba Remote be ham dastresi darand.

1. Server:
1.1 Create Interface ---> bayad Extends Remote
1.2 Creat a Class -----> Implement Interface
                  -----> extends UnicastRemoteObject
2. Client :
2.1 Create Same Interface

!!! Bayad beine Client va Server bayad ye tavafoghi bashad ----> Interface

***************************************'

Be interface haie ke hichi darone anha nist ---> Marker interface ya tak interface migoyand.


